!Greater Rage (Ex)
At 11th level, a barbarian’s bonuses to Strength and Constitution during his {{Homebrew/Barbarian/Rage||modal}} each increase to +6, and his morale bonus on Will saves increases to +3. The penalty to AC remains at -2.